{"tid":1550240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日27-32度 著smart casual 會唔會熱死。。","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T18:37:23.000Z","uid":78683,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1f84e6c56a74a0d0b9ffab2ac0dfb6c2e6b154b6","tid":1550240,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4UQ3MG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4UQ3MG.gif&h=6204fca6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKpULZ2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKpULZ2.gif&h=0689b625&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ab25beb0e490e7c1a4789488565e36bd7aa2eb7","tid":1550240,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1bd2c17daf71d02185076795e7915803a3fcaa","tid":1550240,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:11:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43a04de96914ee9cc5c123fad8b65c2facb0e725","tid":1550240,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:11:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">九月八日 聽日呀！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1:30pm遮打 ----&gt;  2pm<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國領事館</span></span> </span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">為美國風災祈禱：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「多里安」Dorian <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在美國造成最少4人死亡</span></span>，南、北卡州超過35萬戶停電。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479270-20190907.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479270-20190907.htm&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=1e7f4234\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479270-20190907.htm&h=d997d1c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479270-20190907.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cbsnews1.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2019/09/05/b6e68e9e-cf87-4f4c-ab1d-437c624fde04/thumbnail/620x349/8be72af29e5199fec55ab9a6fe7f51a4/0905-ctm-dorianbahamas-begnaud-1927196-640x360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcbsnews1.cbsistatic.com%2Fhub%2Fi%2Fr%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2Fb6e68e9e-cf87-4f4c-ab1d-437c624fde04%2Fthumbnail%2F620x349%2F8be72af29e5199fec55ab9a6fe7f51a4%2F0905-ctm-dorianbahamas-begnaud-1927196-640x360.jpg&h=6aa446ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 唱<span style=\"color: red;\">美</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國</span>國歌(快d聽熟！) 、揮<span style=\"color: red;\">美</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國</span>國旗！！！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=d8b4055f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"88a728b2c3043319d70e0dfed698f26cb8b2e152","tid":1550240,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ab25beb0e490e7c1a4789488565e36bd7aa2eb7","tid":1550240,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:13:02.000Z","msg":"Yo<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1f5QjkD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1f5QjkD.gif&h=243d91f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6rcxFE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6rcxFE.gif&h=436031aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6ccaec9e8213b3001e8628a928650e840ddbe0f","tid":1550240,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88a728b2c3043319d70e0dfed698f26cb8b2e152","tid":15502